overview: Electronic Cigarette “smoking” or “vaping” is getting more and more famous these days. It is not just a great alternative for traditional cigar smoking, it also is proven to not be as harmful as tobaccos and traditional smoke. As people use electronic cigars regularly nowadays, they are now looking for the best electronic cigarette that can satisfy their cravings, affordable, offers a great deal and produces a great amount of vapor. So many brands and models today that meets all of these criteria except not all are affordable. There is one I know that meets all of these criteria, and it is the Joye Ego. There are 3 models that are about the same, the Totally Wicked Tornado, Janty Ego and the Joye Ego. Although these three are relatively the same, there are some little differences that might help you decide on which one is better for you to purchase.
